settings.description: An old test level developed in July of 2021, mainly created to test how Bowser statues react to certain properties. Rel: 1/21/2023, 12:10pm ... #8992-062, also, Happy New Year!
Luigi must take the hammer bro suit on his airship and take it to bowser.
You find yourself in an unknown dimension, and you must find your ship. Will you escape, or will you stay here forever?
Mario goes through the starting area of Bowser's Airship and must defeat boom boom. Bowsers airship 2 is next.
